
OCaml library that wraps the Cassandra interface generated by thrift.

Compiling
=========

(1) set the THRIFT and THRIFT_INCLUDE env. vars to point to the thrift
executable and the directory where the OCaml Thrift library (and .cmi
interface files) resides, respectively.

(2) run

    omake

Example:

   THRIFT=/tmp/thrift/compiler/cpp/thrift \
   THRIFT_INCLUDE=/tmp/thrift/lib/ocaml/src/ \
     omake --verbose

Usage
=====
See cassandra.mli.
